      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Whatsoever ye shall bind on earth ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— By excommunication, pronounced in the Spirit and power of Christ; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "whatsoever ye shall loose — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "By absolution from that sentence. See note on chap. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 16:19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". In the primitive church, absolution meant no more than a discharge from church censure. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Again I say ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— And not only your intercession for the penitent, but all your united prayers, shall be heard. How great then is the power of joint prayer! ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "If two of you ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Suppose a man and his wife. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Where two or three are gathered together in my name ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— That is, to worship me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "I am in the midst of them ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— By my Spirit, to quicken their prayers, guide their counsels, and answer their petitions.",
        "children": []
