        "text": " should have been the subject of the principal clause of the sentence, but was attracted to the subordinate clause and joined to ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "πράγματος",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", so that without the attraction the passage would run thus: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἐὰν δύο ὑμ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
