      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "qua",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " apostles, with ecclesiastical authority, but ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "qua",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " disciples, with the ethical power of morally disciplined men. The Twelve for the moment are for Jesus = the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "ecclesia",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ": they were the nucleus of it. The binding and loosing generically = exercising judgment on conduct; here specifically = treating sin as pardonable or the reverse—a particular exercise of the function of judging.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
